feat: entity tool executor with search and update tools (hr-cax.2)

Implements internal/tools/entities.go with 6 LLM-callable tools:
- find_person: search persons by name, email, phone, or alias
- update_person: create or update person records
- find_place: search places by name, address, or type
- add_thing: create or update things (objects, projects, concepts)
- relate_entities: upsert relationships between any entity pair
- search_entities: full-text search across all entity types using
  PostgreSQL ts_rank with ILIKE fallback

All tools implement the agent.Tool interface (Name, Description,
InputSchema, Execute) for direct registration with the agent loop.
EntityStore.Tools() returns all tools for convenient registration.
